QuestData.Title: Missing Demon
QuestData.Description: I seem to have misplaced my imp, Daglop.$b$bIf you see him, tell him to check in.$b$bNormally I would just resummon him but I'm worried blind Marius here will kill him first and ask questions later.$b$bNo vision, that one.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak with Daglop in the Olivian Veil.
QuestData.RewardText: Yeah yeah, the new master sent you. I get it. I have to deal with my former master first.
